    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1903-11-04T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1903-11-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="233"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d233">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Ehrman</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-11-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 4, 1903</hi>.</date>
                        <lb/>(Received 9.50 a.m.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Cables <hi rend="italic">Nashville</hi> received. <hi rend="italic"
                        >Nashville</hi> notified. Troops will not be moved. Last night gunboat <hi
                        rend="italic">Bogotá</hi> fired several shells on city; one Chinaman killed.
                        <hi rend="italic">Bogotá</hi> threatens bombard city to-day.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Ehrman.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
